text: Iphinopsis choshiensis is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Cancellariidae, the nutmeg snails. ==Description== The shell size varies between 3 mm and 5 mm ==Distribution== This species occurs in the seas off Japan. ==References== ==External links== * Category:Cancellariidae Category:Gastropods described in 1958
title: Iphinopsis choshiensis
